#Aquaman  #lessthan3 #tamilreview

Aquaman review in Tamil |Review Preview |Jason Momoa,Amber Heard
Aquaman tamil review
Aquaman must retrieve the legendary Trident of Atlan to save the underwater city of Atlantis -- and the surface world -- from his power-hungry brother.

Who Is Aquaman? Aquaman is a Superhero from DC Comics. Aquaman character is created by Paul Norris and Mort Weisinger. Aquaman was first seen in the comics in the year 1941. He made his entry in More Fun comics #73. Aquaman is the founder of Justice League. In the 90’s Aquaman was depicted as the King of Atlantis. Aquaman’s name is Arthur Curry. Aquaman’s first appearance in the silver screen is in the year 1967 and the film is The Superman/ Aquaman Hour of Adventure. To know more about Aquaman, do watch the video.
 
Directed by James Wan
Starring         Jason Momoa, Amber Heard, Willem Dafoe,  Patrick Wilson,  Dolph 
                         Lundgren,  Yahya Abdul-Mateen II, Nicole Kidman
Music by Rupert Gregson-Williams
